PRIVACY POLICY
updated October 12, 2020
Welcome to "PersoApps" app’s privacy policy! This policy describes how we collect, use, process and share informations that we collects about you when you use this app. If you have any concerns about this privacy policy you should not use this app.
Data that may be collected
App usage
Navigation inside the app, actions in the app such as clicks on buttons, duration of sessions, frequency of use...
This data is generally analyzed through aggregated reports.
Technical data
ad identifiers, IP address, device country or language, device screen size, operating system and version…
Others datas
If you contact us, for instance by email, we may keep a record of that correspondence.
Your interactions with us on our social media channels.
