Why Do we Collect data ?
Like most of the other app publishers, we need to perform some research, analysis and marketing tasks :
Debug and crash analysis
Detecting/Protecting against security event
Product development/improvement
Advertising,
Preventing fraud and abuse of our policies
Datas collection
The database contains some datas entered by users of this application.
All datas are located only on the devices of users.
Camera usage
The camera (use of android.permission.CAMERA) is used if the user wants take photo to supply content to the app.
Advertisments
This app does have only non-personalized Admob ads. Although non-personalized ads don’t use cookies or mobile ad identifiers for ad targeting, they do still use cookies or mobile ad identifiers for frequency capping, aggregated ad reporting, and to combat
    fraud and abuse.
In-app purchasing
This app makes use of in-app purchasing to remove ads.
